data.description: Immaculate 3 bdrm, 3 full bath Ralph Smucker custom built home filled with gorgeous updates and scenic views located on 1.18 acres in the Jonathon Alder School District. This Ranch features an open layout, natural light throughout, beautiful neutral kitchen, large great room adjacent to eating area, 1st floor laundry & huge garage. Enjoy approx 1300 sq feet in the newly finished basement, that includes 2 separate rooms w/spacious closets, a full bath, & it's own exit to back yard. Enjoy the breathtaking yard on your 620 sq ft Trek Deck, covered front porch, or fully fenced in back yard. Professional landscaping w/back yard fire pit. Views of public golf course from front yard. This well loved home has been beautifully maintained and updated throughout. A must see!!
